PrecisTransfer to the Department of EMPLOYMENT AND IMMIGRATION the control and supervision of the STUDENT ASSISTANCE BRANCH, the OFFICE OF THE ASSISTANT UNDER SECRETARY OF STATE, the INCOME SECURITY PROGRAMS BRANCH and the SOCIAL SERVICE PROGRAMS BRANCH and transfer to the MINISTER all the powers, duties and functions of the MINISTER OF LABOUR and to AMALGAMATE and COMBINE the Department of Employment and Immigration and the Department of Labour under the Minister and the Deputy Minister of Employment and Immigration.
